formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1) This certificate is given based on documents and information provided to us along with Form 4 architect certificate, Building Usage certificate and affidavit of Promoter.
2) Promoter is carrying out more than one site which are registered under GUJRERA. 
As accounts are not maintained project wise, it was not possible to work out exact Cost incurred and paid for Project 
Raghukul Parisar. Further Land of project is not owned by promoter so the amount collected 
in respect of land directly given to Land owner and not passed through RERA bank account.
The cost of land shown in estimate is buying cost of land owner and also not considered index value along with feeling and development cost 
while submitting estimate. so the amount of land value collected by owner seems very high as compared to estimated land cost. 
Therefore it seems that promoter has withdrawn above 70% of estimated cost incurred and paid.
3) Promoter has not executed agreement to sale instead had executed sale deed.
